# This Dockerfile is no longer needed since core is now a library module.
# The core module is imported and used by CLI applications, not run as a standalone service.
# 
# If you need to containerize a CLI application that uses this core:
# 1. Create a new CLI project
# 2. Import the core module as a dependency
# 3. Build your CLI application with its own Dockerfile
#
# For development, use docker-compose.yml to run just the PostgreSQL database.